Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:16.29,comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs30\c&H00747C88\fad(2000,500)\fn@華康流葉體\b1\fsp5\frz-90\pos(570.801,132.666)}這樣走下去該多好……
