Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,槙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 大垣前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,基礎練習結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,結果那孩子啊 把日期搞錯了
