Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:23.94,comment,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLanTingHei-M-GBK\c&H00425867\bord0\fs56\t(\fs55)\pos(280.4,420)}『唯一知曉的妳』
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,想睡的話就睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我會叫醒妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很捨不得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天就沒睡多久 因為太期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是小孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣一直不叫醒她 似乎也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,…該換車了喔
